{
  "stem": "7160.1",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I couldn't standed the hunger anymore.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I-- my feet were swelling and everything.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It was about five, six months after that-- that we were in camp.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[CRYING] So-- so I-- I couldn't-- I couldn't resist the hunger.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was-- I was seeing things, you know, like, mirage in front of me.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I mean, hunger and hungry is different, where you eat one day, two days is hunger.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But when you don't eat for months in and months out, this is what hunger is.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You-- everything you see, seems like it's food.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Even-- even a-- a round stone looks like food, like it is a potato.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I took a rush over there, and I run into the-- to the thing over there.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I look around, and nobody is watching me.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I run, and I grab a couple of potatoes from over there, and I tried to run back to the-- to the-- where the people were working, digging.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "One was an Ukrainian-- Ukrainian-- the one he was escaped people from-- from the Russia army.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he come voluntarily to the German army-- an Ukrainian soldier.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But he become an-- an-- an SS soldier.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He saw me doing that.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He took-- he put the rifle to shoot me.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The gun jam.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So he-- he turned the gun around, and he starts swinging the gun at me like-- like I was hitting a-- a pillow-- those heavy, old fashioned guns.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He hit me one in they knee, and the knee was totally dislocated.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The knee got this side.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So then two or three times I-- I-- the-- I dive a few times not to hit.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Then he was-- he hit me right with it, right on the mouth, here.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
